column5: Can anyone give directions to the beer depot in Fort Frances or does anyone know if there is one in Dryden? Also what are the hours for these stores?
Did you mean the Beer Store? If so, here you go. Fort Franceshttp://www.thebeerstore.ca/ourstores...ils.asp?id=432 Drydenhttp://www.thebeerstore.ca/ourstores...ils.asp?id=980
For beer, liquor, locations and hours of operation try this link...http://www.lcbo.com/lcbo-ear/jsp/storequery.jsp
